{"type": "article", "id": 6968, "title": "怎样从迷糊中完全醒来？", "description": null, "date": "1970-01-01T00:00:00Z", "super_tag": null, "tags": [], "category": null, "author": 1317, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 1, "image": "img/default_images/missing_article.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t最后，无论是晚睡、午睡、公车睡，怎样才能在迷糊之中迅速醒来？\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t跟着我一起做。首先，将“好奇心日报”的应用放到首屏；然后在醒来的迷糊中打开它；我相信你马上会被标题亮瞎了双眼（或者找到什么有趣的内容想点开）！\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t不要犹豫！\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t好奇心日报（支持 <a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/hao-qi-xin-ri-bao/id919052037?mt=8\" target=\"_blank\">iPhone</a> 以及 <a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.qdaily.ui&amp;hl=zh\" target=\"_blank\">Android</a>）\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160604214019nrH78IUBpdJ3ksFQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.529\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\n\n\n"}